description: Removes one or more tags from the specified resource.

parameters.name: ResourceArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the canary or group that you're removing tags from. The ARN format of a canary is ``arn:aws:synthetics:Region:account-id:canary:canary-name ``. The ARN format of a group is arn:aws:synthetics:Region:account-id:group:group-name.

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: The list of tag keys to remove from the resource. (string) ---
